    "Management": {
      "text": "Non-Operative\nUp to 30 degrees angulation is well tolerated\nLong arm posterior splint\n,\nsling and swathe splint\n, or\ncoaptation splint\nROM exercises in 2-3 weeks\nOperative\nOpen fractures\nIpsilateral forearm injury \"Floating elbow\"\nShoulder injury or poly trauma",
